🔹 Azure Boards – Must-Remember Points
Work Item Hierarchy
Epic → Feature → User Story → Task → Bug

Boards Use Cases
    Sprint planning
    Velocity tracking
    Linking: Commit → Build → Release → Work Item

🔹 Azure Repos – Git Exam Notes
Supported
    Git (preferred)
    TFVC (legacy)
Branch Policies (VERY IMPORTANT)
    Mandatory PR review
    Build validation
    Minimum reviewers
    Prevent direct pushes to main
